wikipedia_page.main: Jessica Anne "Jess" Roberts (born 11 April 1999) is a British cyclist, who currently rides for UCI Women's WorldTeam Team BikeExchange. She won the British National Road Race Championships in 2018. Her sister, Amy Roberts is also a professional cyclist.
